Unna paathu sirichaa 
Adha ullukkulla nerupaakku

adhil greedam onna uruvaakku

aanandham adayume

Nee unakku sollum aaraaro 
Kan thoongi ezhundha pinbu nee vero

Kizhinja vedhayile thaan kaadu porakkume

Roohe nee akalum munbuppane kandu marikkenam.
Allekil ummantte koode marikkenam.
Roohe nee piriyum munbuppane kandu marikkenam.
Vidhiyundel uppantte koode madagenam.
Ee mannil thunanigal pakaliravil punjagal...
Cheru novum ariyunnor.
Nira sneham pakarunnor.
Vanathil keezhe eni ennennum thudarenam...
     (Roohe..)

Thalarathe thakarathe duniyavil thanalayi ee ummantte nizhalayi ennum njanille.
Cherukudilil padavukalil mizhi edarathoru thiriyayi enn varavennum kaakkanoru nizhalayi neeyille.
Niramazhayil eriveyilil oru kudayay njanille.
Oru karuthal kadalakan ennuppa koottunde.
Niraravil nilav pozhinjath poloru sneham pakarunne.
Kalichiriyil kadha parayan  ennumma koodunde.
Kadhanathil karamekan ennuppa koottunde.
     (Roohe...)

Kaalathin oolethil ozhukunne cheruvanchi.
Athinerathii snehathin thuzhayayi njanunde.
Oru kattil ulayathe oru thirayil thakarathe ee janmathil kadavil thunayakanivanundo.
Oru theeyayi anayunnor ee maanava janmagal.
Oru theeyum pozhiyathe pakarami snehagal.
Udayorith ummayuppayum ulakiluyiril swasagal.
Oru puzhathan thelineeram ee sneham pakaramo.
Oru kadalin alapole ee sneham pakaramo.

Rescuers are racing to save people trapped beneath the rubble after hundreds of buildings collapsed in both countries.¬†

World leaders have pledged to send aid after Turkey issued an international appeal for help.¬†

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3687 - 6 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3687: Jhoot Ka Jaal
--------------------------------------------------------
Bapuji shares his story about how he escaped with everybody at Gokuldham. He never went to the park, and that is why Jetha and Sodhi never found him there; instead, he was at the clubhouse. When Champaklal was heading towards the park, he came across Tapu Sena and decided to play tennis at the clubhouse. When Tapu Sena and Champaklal saw Taarak's boss from the balcony, they immediately hid him. Champaklal tore off the head of the brand-new floor mop, which Abdul bought and wore as a hair wig. Everyone at Gokuldham was impressed by Champaklal's impromptu idea. Stay tuned to learn more!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3687, 6 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

Think about the situation where all her dreams are crumbling before her eyes, Ganga enters her life as a thousand dreams like this. But when she realized that her dreams were not reality, Ganga was not ready to give up even though she was tired like anyone else. Even though many opportunities have passed through her life that could have weakened him, she did not get tired and took time for herself, and the journey that started with a firm decision that's she will not lose has reached Josh talks with us today. This story will definitely help you to decide that the story of Ganga can be the story of many of us, nothing is the end of anything, but it is an opportunity to prove yourself.

If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalis. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women‚Äôs rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. Tere Bin Episode 12 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 2nd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

In this historic event that broke the Asian record for most students gathered. Gurudev answered questions that came in from all the college and university students that had gathered from across Pune. The questions ranged from career choices to drugs to breakups and a very interesting rapid fire round at the end.

About #Gurudev - 
World-renowned humanitarian, spiritual leader, and an ambassador of peace and human values. Gurudev founded The Art of Living, a non-profit organization that is engaged in stress-management and service initiatives across the world.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3686 - 4 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3686: Bade Guruji
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak's boss notices Bapuji standing at the clubhouse's balcony, and he is taken aback. He tells Taarak that he saw Badey Guruji in Gokuldham, but Taarak denies it. He says that Badey Guruji is at Haridwar, so it must be an illusion. Taarak's adamant boss climbs up to the clubhouse to find out the truth. Initially, Tapu Sens tries to prevent the boss from entering the clubhouse, but later they fail to stop him. After searching every nook and cranny, Taarak's boss finds someone's shoes peeping out from behind the curtains. What will happen if Taarak's boss discovers the truth? Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3686, 4 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:
Filmmaker-actor K Viswanath passed away in Hyderabad on Thursday. In a career spanning six decades,  K Viswanath visualized themes like Telugu culture, Telugu Music, the caste system, untouchability, gender discrimination, dowry and socio-economic challenges in his movies. Chelleli Kapuram, Kalam Marindi, Sarada, O Seeta Katha Jeevana Jyothi, Siri Siri Muvva, Sankarabharanam, Saptapadi, Sagara Sangamamm, Swathi Muthyam, Sruthilayalu, Swarnakamalam, Sutradharulu, Aapadbhandhuvudu, Swati Kiranam, Subha Sankalpam, Swarabhishekam, Sargam, Kaamchor, Shubh Kaamna, Eeshwar and Dhanwaan are few of his acclaimed films. 

We must noted,  K Viswanath movie Swathi Muthyam was picked as India‚Äôs official entry for the Oscars in 1986. He worked with Kamal Haasan, Jayaprada, Rishi Kapoor, Anil Kapoor, Vanisri and Chiranjeevi among others.

snippet.title: INDIAN BUDGET EXPLAINED IN 10 MINUTES | Budget 2023 explained | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain the process in which the Union Budget is made and take a look at some of the top spends in the 2023 Union Budget

The Budget is an important document because it signifies the direction that the Government wants to take. It gives a chance to the people to see which ministry takes up most of the resources and understand how much money the Government makes and where they spend it. It is time all of us analyze the data and ask the Government the right questions. 

This video will help you demystify the Budget process and understand the basics of this event

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

#budget2023 #finance #economy 

Stay ahead of the game with our exclusive coverage of the Indian Budget 2023. Our in-depth analysis breaks down the latest fiscal policies, economic indicators and their impact on citizens and businesses. Get a complete rundown of government spending and revenue, including allocation for key sectors such as education, health, infrastructure, and more. With expert insights and easy to understand explanations, our video is the go-to source for staying informed on the Indian Budget 2023. Watch now to stay ahead of the curve and make informed decisions.

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

After Sankar tears Thapki's dress and pushes her into a tank filled with water, Bihaan comes to her rescue. Bihaan finally gets over his fear of Holi and applies colour on Thapki, while a jealous Sankar watches on with rage. What will be Sankar's next move?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

Qalandar Episode 34 - [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Komal Meer - Ali Abbas - Hiba Aziz - 4th February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Qalandar is a story of a girl‚Äôs firm belief in her God and His decisions while the rest of the world continues to hurt, defame and challenge her.

Dur-e-Adan is a young and innocent girl who has grown up under the care of her uncle and aunt. Despite being an orphan at an early age, Dur-e-Adan doesn‚Äôt complain about her challenges and difficulties.

On the contrary, Tabriz is a handsome young man who aspires to achieve great things in life. Living in the same locality, Tabriz‚Äôs parents find Dur-e-Adan suitable for him as a life partner. However, Tabriz‚Äôs life takes a surprising turn when Sumbul hailing from a wealthy family falls in love with him. In efforts to secure his future financially, Tabriz forgets the gift that he has been bestowed in the form of Dur-e-Adan for this world and hereafter. Soon, Tabriz‚Äôs half-heartedness and conflicting loyalties in the form of greed begins to reflect in his relationship with Dur-e-Adan.

Amidst all the atrocities faced by Dur-e-Adan will she continue to be patient with those around her? Will Tabriz realize the respect and love that Dur-e-Adan deserves or will he continue to hurt her? Will Tabriz be able to mend his relationship with Dur-e-Adan?

Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.description:
Karan, a dreaded gangster, falls in love with Kajal, the daughter of his nemesis Prof. Siddharth. After initial hesitation Kajal reciprocates Karans advances and tries to reform him with her love. However, Prof. Siddharth forces Kajal to marry Raju, the son of his childhood friend, Ramakanth. Thus, Karan returns to his violent old days after suffering the heartbreak. Watch to know what transpires when Karan finds out that Raju is his next target. Will Karan kill Raju or stand guard for him against the odds?Watch to know more.  Watch to know more.  

Movie - Jeet (1996)
StarCast - Salman Khan, Sunny Deol, Karishma Kapoor, Tabu, Amrish Puri, Alok Nath
Director - Raj Kanwar
Producer - Sajid Nadiadwala
Cinematography - A. Muthu
Editor - Harmeet Singh

localized.description:
Karan, a dreaded gangster, falls in love with Kajal, the daughter of his nemesis Prof. Siddharth. After initial hesitation Kajal reciprocates Karans advances and tries to reform him with her love. However, Prof. Siddharth forces Kajal to marry Raju, the son of his childhood friend, Ramakanth. Thus, Karan returns to his violent old days after suffering the heartbreak. Watch to know what transpires when Karan finds out that Raju is his next target. Will Karan kill Raju or stand guard for him against the odds?Watch to know more.  Watch to know more.
